is\nyear, as examples.\nForrest Easterly\nEnlisted In Navy\nForrest Orley Easterly, son of Mi\nami Mrs. H. M. Martin Easterly o:\nBrownsville, was selected from\namong 400 applicants in the S ii\nTexas district to join the navy, nc\ncerding to George Kramer, recruit\ning officer.\nNo boy with less than a high\nschool education is taken but East\nerly also had one year in Browns\nville Junior college.\nThere is only one negro mem\nber of the U. S. Congress. He is\nOscar De Priest, Republican from\nChicago.\nRoad Association\nMeets in Houston\nWith prospects o:: her than\never, tne Hug-the-Coost highway\nassociat.on will meet in Houston\nrhur^juy in joint session with two\nother road bodies, it has been an\nnounced uy cgt O. C. Dancy, a\ndirc:.< r in the association.\nH. C. Innis, secretary of the\nbody, states in a letttr to Judge\n1 Dancy: \u201cThere are so many things\nto encourage us that we ought to\nlook to the future with much\nconf ide ace. Copano buy is high\nbridged, the crossing over Lavaca\nEnds Headache\nIn One-Half\nUsual Time\nCEADACHES from nerves or eye:\nor stomach, pains that f* llow\nlard, tedious work, can be reltevec\nwith licile delay. Capudine, a iquic\npreparation is the new, ama. ingly\njuick way that is replacing ordinary\npowders aud tablets.\ntn thousands of homes it has become\nt house a dd remedy kept on hand ai\ndl times to end suffering and misery\ntom headaches.\nJeing liquid, Capudine acts immedi\nately, olten in one-third the tune re\nluired by otner forms, it contains nc\nlarcotics, does not disturb digest 10c\naid is approved by doctors and drug\n'ists. Even with the most seven\nicadache, relief comes very quickly\nold at Drcu Store*. 10c. Klc. sod 60c bottle\n\u2022ad bi the dot at soda lou.ita.ac\n\n-Sl\nbay is gougg ahead with dispatch:\ngrading and dint work are in\nprogress from Copano crossing\nnorth toward Tivoli; Brazoria\ncounty is working Galveston county\nwilt se? that we have a road from\nthere to Orange.\u201d\nOVER 